'''阿夫林州'''（{{Lang-en|Afrin Canton}}；{{Lang-ku|Kantona Efrînê}}），是[[北叙利亚民主联邦|北叙利亚民主联邦]]四个州和地区中最西边的一個，2014年1月宣布自治。<ref name="mednuce">{{Cite web|url = http://mednuce.com/en//haber/2344/democratic-autonomy-has-declared-in-afrin-canton-in-rojava.html|title = Democratic autonomy has declared in Afrin canton in Rojava|publisher = Mednuce|accessdate = 23 October 2014|date = 29 January 2014|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180706022020/http://mednuce.com/en//haber/2344/democratic-autonomy-has-declared-in-afrin-canton-in-rojava.html|archive-date = 2018-07-06|dead-url = yes}}</ref><ref name="firat">{{Cite web|url = http://supportkurds.org/news/monday-27-january-2013/|title = After Cizîre, Kobanê Canton has been declared|publisher = Firat News|accessdate = 23 October 2014|archive-date = 2014-09-20|archive-url = https://archive.is/20140920090656/http://supportkurds.org/news/monday-27-january-2013/|dead-url = no}}</ref>行政中心位於[[阿夫林_(敘利亞)|阿夫林]]<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://civiroglu.net/the-constitution-of-the-rojava-cantons/|title = The Constitution of the Rojava Cantons; Personal Website of Mutlu Civiroglu|publisher = civiroglu.net|accessdate = 23 October 2014|archive-date = 2014-06-22|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140622054728/http://civiroglu.net/the-constitution-of-the-rojava-cantons/|dead-url = no}}</ref>，現任總理是{{le|希非·易卜拉欣|Hêvî Îbrahîm}}。阿夫林州人口主要為[[庫德族|庫德族]]，該州在[[叙利亚内战|叙利亚内战]]中受到附近[[征服沙姆阵线|征服沙姆阵线]]<ref>{{Cite news|title = Syria's Kurds Warn Afrin Could Be The New Kobani|url = http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/11/07/syria-afrin_n_6121632.html|accessdate = 2015-11-09|archive-date = 2014-12-12|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141212163438/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/11/07/syria-afrin_n_6121632.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>和[[土耳其|土耳其]]<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/2018-01/21/c_1122289585.htm |title=土耳其宣布发起对叙利亚阿夫林的军事行动 |publisher=新華網 |date=2018-01-21}}</ref>的威脅。

== 行政當局 ==
