== 歷史 ==
Stefan Sperl指出，有理由相信庫德山區在[[塞琉古|塞琉古]]時代就有庫德人居住，因為該地位在往[[安提阿|安提阿]]的路徑上。庫德人在過去常擔任僱傭兵和騎射手。<ref name="sperl">{{Cite book|last1 = Kreyenbroek|first1 = P.G.|last2 = Sperl|first2 = S.|title = The Kurds: A Contemporary Overview|year = 1992|url = https://books.google.nl/books?id=JZ6JAgAAQBAJ&pg=PA116#v=onepage&q&f=false|publisher = Routledge|isbn = 0415072654|pages = 116}}</ref>

2018年1月20日，土耳其發起「[[橄欖枝行動|橄欖枝行動]]」入侵阿夫林州，並於3月攻入其行政中心[[阿夫林|阿夫林]]。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2018-03/18/c_1122554725.htm |title=土耳其称已控制叙利亚阿夫林市中心 |publisher=新華網 |date=2018-03-18}}</ref>

== 經濟 ==
由於[[土耳其|土耳其]]對阿夫林州實施禁運，對阿夫林州的人民產生影響巨大<ref>{{Cite news|script-title =tr:Rojava’dan ikazlar|url = http://www.cumhuriyet.com.tr/haber/dunya/242591/Rojava_dan_ikazlar.html#|publisher = Cumhuriyet}}</ref>。

經濟以農業為主，尤其是[[小麥|小麥]]<ref name="afrin">{{Cite web|title = Agriculture Commission is Looking at the Process of Receiving Wheat from Farmers|url = http://cantonafrin.com/en/news/view/1123.agriculture-commission-is-looking-at-the-process-of-receiving-wheat-from-farmers.html|website = Afrin Canton|accessdate = 13 June 2015|archive-date = 2015-06-14|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150614131849/http://cantonafrin.com/en/news/view/1123.agriculture-commission-is-looking-at-the-process-of-receiving-wheat-from-farmers.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

